{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers must choose the most suitable validation approach based on their specific experimental context.",
    "Continuous advancements and the introduction of innovative comparison methodologies have the potential to enhance the comprehensive evaluation of robustness and accuracy over time.",
    "Benchmark resultsBased on the aforementioned datasets and evaluation methods, we conduct benchmarks to compare the performance of LiDAR-only odometry and LiDAR-inertial odometry.",
    "Our benchmark test analyzes the performance of six LiDARonly odometry and six LiDAR-inertial odometry literature.",
    "For LiDAR-only odometry, the selected methods are LOAM [162], LeGO-LOAM [125], KISS-ICP [137], CT-ICP [31], and DLO [20]."
  ]
}